data.description: Located in the esteemed Acacia Grove, this lovely 3-level townhome w/striking stone & brick accents is the one! Discover a sizable open floor plan on the second floor bathed in sunlight & has balcony access, perfect for morning coffees. With its tall ceilings, designer's palette, plantation shutters, & walnut hardwood flooring, this home exudes charm. The kitchen is fully equipped w/ample counter space, a pantry, an island, a breakfast bar, & handsome crown molding cabinetry. Practical den w/built-in shelves. Ascend to the third level & be impressed by the generous main retreat, highlighting a plush carpet, a full ensuite w/dual sinks, a separate tub, a walk-in closet, & an incredible view outside. Secondary bedrooms downstairs enjoy soft carpets & mirrored door closets. Don't miss out!
